<br>
This guild has many a famous bard<br>
Who has become strong, through working quite hard<br>
Who can lay waste to enemies like the devil,<br>
And is now ready, of an appropriate level,<br>
<br>
To fight, to die, to take on great foes<br>
To go into their lairs and bring them great woes,<br>
But though we be troubadors tough and self-made,<br>
We need other people with whom to raid!<br>
<br>
(/ooc now)<br>
<br>
Some Background:<br>
Molto Espressivo is an all-bard guild.  We got together about 8 months ago, and are mostly veterans of other servers.  We endeavor as much as possible to group together, level together, and help each other out.  It's a neat group, with some very interesting and exciting possibilities.  The versatility of bards allows for some really neat tactics, and we've had a lot of fun doing this.<br>
<br>
We are limited in one respect, however.  While we can do quite a bit of dungeon crawling and outdoor fighting, we lack the numbers and the necessary tools to raid.  At earlier levels, this was not much of a concern to us, but now that a full group of us are in their late 40's up to 54 with several AA's, the time has come for us to make raiding available to our players.<br>
<br>
What I would like to propose is an open partnership with any and all raiding guilds, so that we would be allowed to come to your raids and have a fair chance at bard-appropriate loot.  By fair chance, I mean to say that you allow us the same opportunities you allow others in your guild of the same level.<br>
<br>
I think this proposition would be a welcome one for most raiding guilds of an appropriate level.  We are all bards, so we're not really going to take much away from your loot tables, and the crowd control, mana regeneration, haste, damage shields, debuffs, DoTs, buff stripping, and enhanced DPS could be very beneficial to any raid you care to do.  We're mostly veterans, and we've been there, and done that before.  We know how raids work, and we're happy filling any role you want us in.<br>
<br>
We are also adept dungeon fighters, and many of us have had significant success in LDoN dungeons.  Though we are as yet too low to do LDoN raids, we're good folks to have in a dungeon crawl.  Look us up if you want to try us out.<br>
<br>
If you're interested in establishing such a partnership, please make an appopriate post to <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub142.ezboard.com/feqdivabardsofeverquestfrm83">pub142.ezboard.com/feqdiv...questfrm83</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Thanks!<br>
<br>
Feroce<br>
